[i]Landfall[/i] – Whenever a land you control enters, put a level counter on Joraga Chieftain.
As long as Joraga Chieftain has two or more level counters on it, Joraga Chieftain and other Elves you control have “{T}: Add {G}.”
As long as Joraga Chieftain has four or more level counters on it, Joraga Chieftain and other Elves you control get +2/+2.
